OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid passes may be used to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fkeep pubs open at Christmas
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Covid passes may be used over Christmas
OL,6, in order to keep pubs and restaurants  
OL,7, open, the Welsh government has said.   
OL,9,FBut First Minister Mark Drakeford said 
OL,10,Fno decision would be made on           
OL,11,Fintroducing the pass to the hospitality
OL,12,Fsector until early December.           
OL,14,FMr Drakeford made the comments as he   
OL,15,Funveiled the latest 21-day review of   
OL,16,FCovid regulations.                     
OL,18,FHe said there would be no rule changes 
OL,19,Fin the next three weeks, following the 
OL,20,Flatest review on Thursday.             
